eted the pre-requisite course in earlier semesters so that they can take the course SI 422 in this semester.\n\nPlease reply asap.\n\nThanks &amp; Regards,\nSaurabh Bhola','7888bcb80966164840aaa269ad3978e5',0,'','38gd3cfd',1,0,'',0,0,0),(228,83,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1324645822,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Mathematics and statistics minor','Please check the minor course structure at \n<!-- m --><a class=\"postlink\" href=\"http://www.math.iitb.ac.in/academic/minor2.html\">http://www.math.iitb.ac.in/academic/minor2.html</a><!-- m -->\n\nGeneral Topology runs every alternate year and would be running next year (every odd year eg. this year 2011-12 is considered to be even as 2012 )','950d97213e4414649b301d4f0e1dce33',0,'','3hfp10gd',1,0,'',0,0,0),(229,85,11,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1324646053,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Minor Course SI 422 : Regression Analysis','Thanks a lot Saurabh, it will be well considered !!','ffdfe436de66b122ceac052a7ada3faf',0,'','1ljvc0wm',1,0,'',0,0,0),(230,83,32,364,0,'10.175.24.181',1324648425,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Mathematics and statistics minor','Hey,\n\nI want to do a course in mathematics (as a minor) which is not officially listed as a minor, but the math department is ready to acknowledge it as a minor. It is not on the list of minor courses to register. Can I register for it later during course registration and tag it as a minor, or do I have to do something now to get it into the list of minor courses?','760e193eeda79dae1a3b9cf5272ae5cf',0,'','3fcon407',1,0,'',0,0,0),(231,84,29,353,0,'10.209.4.1',1324658543,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Department Elective and Course Tagging','And will i be able to tag it whenever the tagging interface opens for our batch (09D).','dba056488e283c70955cdb4d00d4b8b0',0,'','1u7wzwl1',1,0,'',0,0,0),(232,84,29,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1324660914,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Department Elective and Course Tagging','Yes you can tag it as a dept. elective at the end of this sem','5857e8907937e532ab8619c7dfb766d4',0,'','2v9uvq9y',1,0,'',0,0,0),(233,83,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1324661054,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Mathematics and statistics minor','You can register for that course as a normal additional learning course and if you are sure  that maths dept. will acknowledge it as minor you can get an application endorsed by HoD Maths signed from Dean AP to effectuate the required tag change later on in the sem','cf4d4f45d4d65c9315563da0ed78040d',0,'','4f1g15u2',1,0,'',0,0,0),(234,85,11,2,0,'10.8.210.55',1324689215,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Minor Course SI 422 : Regression Analysis','Thanks  for the clarification .. <!-- s:-) --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon/smile.gif\" alt=\":-)\" title=\"Smile\" /><!-- s:-) -->','3ad0f56460a079f6b09beda627ef13d5',0,'','3blqy9xs',1,0,'',0,0,0),(235,86,32,371,0,'10.209.4.2',1324720608,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Minor Courses in Chemistry','In the list of courses offered for minor, none of the courses of either Chemical Engineering Department, not of the Department of Chemistry, are being offered, although the mail from the Dean AP\'s office claims that all the courses from all the departments which are being offered for minor, are shown in the list. Please clarify on this matter. Will there be any minor courses from these departments?\n\nThank You','2b5190609847a40e74e4dcf96bc8d405',0,'','3v9nmceg',1,0,'',0,0,0),(236,87,9,340,0,'10.209.4.1',1324906824,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','CS minor course','Hi,\n\nThe list of minor courses for CS  being offered this semester has not been updated  till now and the deadline for minor registration is almost over. I have done the following CS minor courses:\n\nCS 207, CS 213, CS 347, CS 348 but in the minor interface it shows only CS 213 and CS 348. Please extend the deadline and update the list.','6f29d28d02041d31cf37f53031ef7893',0,'','1xm7wsaj',1,0,'',0,0,0),(237,87,9,61,0,'10.199.2.27',1325060689,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: CS minor course','I am afraid the third course will not be running due to lack of faculty and we are looking to provide an alternative for completion of your minor degree (