e need to complete 2 6 credit courses and 18 credit BTP. My question is can we take one of the 2 courses in our 8th sem rather than taking it in the 6th as the sem load is already heavy??','b0a46d04f1cbf0a1e67c911f7ecd17d9',0,'','9ekls2dn',1,0,'',0,0,0),(245,91,32,390,0,'10.209.4.2',1325221349,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Error in registration for MG401 minor','I have been allotted MG401 as minor. But while registering I am getting registration rule exception and this is the error:\n&quot;Registration limit is reached! This course can be taken by limited number of students. Any further registrations must be done with instructor\'s consent through manual adjustment form available in Academic office.&quot;\n\nThis error shouldn\'t have come as I have been allotted MG401 as minor. There seems to be some mistake.\nWhy is this error coming? What should I do about it?','16ac6398e6e5f34ea6eff3629c929f1a',0,'','3uqv5zwj',1,0,'',0,0,0),(246,92,10,391,0,'10.209.4.1',1325223363,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Change of HSS elective','According to the preferences asked,I have been alloted Proffessional ethics as an HSS insti elective.In case I want to change it to another one what steps do I need to follow??','d9fe5aaa68741fe6c39a5dc940c07be4',0,'','2yxgkpu6',1,0,'',0,0,0),(247,91,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325225772,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Error in registration for MG401 minor','Please check now !!','d81a9f190e19fb86cc553b984ca2d305',0,'','771wyao7',1,0,'',0,0,0),(248,92,10,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325226094,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Change of HSS elective','You need to register for the other course under the Additional Courses /Extra Courses heading on your ASC interface. Put the tag as institute elective.','897540b813d9ac476180bf9980ee900a',0,'','1s7bivqu',1,0,'',0,0,0),(249,93,32,383,0,'10.3.70.68',1325226331,1,0,1,1,1,0,'','CONVERT ADDITIONAL COURSE TO MINOR','I m DD student. For last sem my cpi was less than 8 so i was unable to take minor course, instead of that i took an additional course. Now for this sem i can take a minor course. So I want to know that is it possible to convert the additional course which i took last sem into a minor course ? \nTo whom I must contact regarding this issue ?','16eea7fdd355ca8fc5ab75343a3e4f65',0,'','1xd476jc',1,0,'',0,0,0),(250,90,14,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325226372,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Honors course in 8th sem','Yes but with following caveats : \n1) Slot clash can happen in 8th sem aslo \n2) Your academic category might change and you may not be able to overload in that sem ( a distant possibility ) \n3) Last sem blues <!-- s:P --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon/razz.gif\" alt=\":P\" title=\"Razz\" /><!-- s:P -->','743cd7d18308587f932b4525db6fc4b3',0,'','2ng8r1mh',1,0,'',0,0,0),(251,93,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325226430,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: CONVERT ADDITIONAL COURSE TO MINOR','I am afraid, you can not do that.','75d63688299d23dfc6eb51f42dc391cd',0,'','2wo88tsv',1,0,'',0,0,0),(252,94,11,394,9,'10.3.114.29',1325233375,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','HSS Electives','Is the grade in HSS elective courses counted in the semester\'s CPI.\n\nWhat is the slot of HSS Elective courses? I could not find it in the institute time-table and there is no time-table on the HSS department\'s site.','9f16313809187f2dbc321381430162fd',0,'','2hlc8315',1,0,'',0,0,0),(253,95,28,395,0,'10.7.143.14',1325235004,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Honors Courses','Is it compulsory to do a given course as honors or you can do any other course from your department and tag it as honors ? As far as I know one needs to do 30 credits in one\'s own department for an Honors. But should the courses be specific or any course can be chosen ? Kindly confirm asap. \n\nThanks','d66386a12ca7003f646a88353762e189',0,'','3pasvabr',1,0,'',0,0,0),(254,96,12,368,0,'10.9.12.58',1325235616,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Credit Requirements','I am trying to register for 46 credits this semester including two additional learning courses. However, I got a message that &quot;	You are not allowed to take this much credit as per the academics rule book. Please de-register from some course(s)&quot;. \nI have an academic standing of Category I and as far as my knowledge is concerned academic rulebook allows a maximum of 48 credits. \nWhat should I do?','049342b0d50b66657167a0d88b30d73a',0,'','v26qva5d',1,0,'',0,0,0),(255,94,11,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325239109,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: HSS Electives','If an HSS elective is mentioned in your curriculum then its grade will be counted in your CPI. If you are taking it as an additional learning then it will not be counted.\n\nYou can check the slots of all the HSS courses through asc.  go to academics -&gt; course info -&gt; running courses','8c480fac64285c401e664c9190e8fefe',0,'','2x43j0ns',1,0,'',0,0,0),(256,96,12,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325239719,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Credit Requirements','please mail your problem to <!-- e --><a href=\"mailto:asc.help@iitb.ac.in\">asc.help@iitb.ac.in</a><!-- e --> if the problem still prevails.','13d6e339390e570e8d9c63eed7e01cde',0,'','1bm0qwl3',1,0,'',0,0,0),(257,95,28,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325239991,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Honors Courses','Please contact your department General Secretary about this problem as it is different for each department.','2a13b171dadd20421522d6c2d46baf67',0,'','movhk11n',1,0,'',0,0,0),(258,95,28,395,0,'10.7.143.14',1325244809,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Honors Courses','Thanks for your prompt response.\n\n One more doubt: \nIn the Additional Courses section on registration interface, the Elective Tag Dropdown box shows two options related to Honors 1- Honor Course  2- Honor Elective Course \n\nWhat is the difference between these two ?','99c114a0a9f8eb5f24d77e021026289d',0,'','8nrwlo10',1,0,'',0,0,0),(259,97,32,324,0,'10.152.50.254',1325249273,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','HS Electives','I am a III year student.\nI secured the course HS 440 (Industrial Economics) as an HS elective through pre-registration. However, I wish to take this course as an institute elective.\nSo, while registering, should I drop this pre-registered HS elective and simultaneously register for it as an institute elective OR can I continue with it as an HS elective and later tag it as my institute elective?\n\nFundamentally, isn\'t an HS elective just another insti elective from the HSS department?\n\nThank you.','7d5bc2a029883ad8ce43775db6cfffc3',0,'','3oerb0fm',1,0,'',0,0,0),(260,97,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325250343,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: HS Electives','HSS electives are a subset of institute electives which are all those courses which are not from your dept. So you need not do anything !','06f54ca6540a4e5d2fe1bc376cc0a833',0,'','l8vicb93',1,0,'',0,0,0),(261,95,28,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325250621,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Honors Courses','Honors course = A specific course that has to be done without without which Honors will not be awarded to you \n\nHonors elective = An elective course for the completion of credit requirements; you could choose from a list of dept. electives in this case which essentially is the floating component of the honors degree','fdc4eee34342f75405228f3fe53902be',0,'','1zpyz34o',1,0,'',0,0,0),(262,98,32,357,0,'10.209.4.1',1325252345,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Doing two minors','is it really possible to do two minors for a student having academic category 1 given the fact that all minor courses run only in slot 5 ?','eac6dd1cf40c3e31260be0809768225b',0,'','3s6kmvbw',1,0,'',0,0,0),(263,98,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325257924,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Doing two minors','I have never come across anybody who has achieved this feat, may  be you can try <!-- s:P --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon/razz.gif\" alt=\":P\" title=\"Razz\" /><!-- s:P --> \nIf the demand for doing 2 minors picks up may be after sometime insti starts having 2 slots for minors.','619a5f3542943066f770171c260edef3',0,'','1zrbpciq',1,0,'',0,0,0),(264,99,32,357,0,'10.209.4.1',1325258803,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Slot clash between core and elective course','I am second year aero BTech student . i want to take one extra additional learning course as insti. elective this semester but in the time table it is written that UG HSS/Insti. elec. courses will run in slot 2 which clashes with the slot given to one of the core courses.','711f4435fba51b419db74b8b97e317f2',0,'','1jqt1r4j',1,0,'',0,0,0),(265,99,32,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325262261,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Slot clash between core and elective course','you can take additional learning/insti elective in any slot you want as long as its slot is not clashing with any other course slot.','ee40d15cd7d0f8ddc9eb23f273bff58c',0,'','372vh0uw',1,0,'',0,0,0),(266,100,32,312,0,'10.8.20.12',1325270641,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Error in registration','When I click the Registration/Adjustment link I get an error &quot;Registration blocked&quot; .\nWhy is that so? What should I do?','5e1f296434881c726fd0824d85723f61',0,'','2ksl9czn',1,0,'',0,0,0),(267,101,28,395,0,'10.7.143.14',1325304855,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Minor Query','Hi !\nI am asking this because the Additional Courses section on ASC registration interface shows MINOR also as an elective tag.\n\nCan one take any other course run by a department than the &quot;prescribed&quot; set of courses and tag it as MINOR in the additional courses section to fulfill credit requirements of a minor?\n\n(Example: Suppose I have been doing all EE courses as MINORS but there is no course in this sem which seems useful to me. So can I take some other course which interests me with permission of instructor and use it to fulfill my credit requirements for MINOR as well so that I can get minor completed? )\n\nIf yes, is there any procedure or one just has to take the course and put elective tag as MINOR ?','58ff6ff520fdc5e5baa1f812964674c2',0,'','1rc6zkph',1,0,'',0,0,0),(268,102,32,399,0,'10.209.4.2',1325307249,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Retagging of courses','Hello,\nI have done an 8-credit maths minor course before, which can be retagged to an institute elective. So, I was wondering about the time around when the retagging interface would open for final-year B.Techs. Also, I presume that I need not take an institute elective this semester in that case?\n\nThank you','bd2fcf3617b5a44fc61ef5255952076b',0,'','2zcpql86',1,0,'',0,0,0),(269,84,29,400,0,'10.7.161.15',1325313930,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Department Elective and Course Tagging','I had taken an insti elective in which i did not get good grade, so I want to replace that course by taking another course in this sem. Which under which tag should I register the extra course, additional learning courses or insti elective ???','0b98bb7643d53970e43da1ecfe53b134',0,'','160kx6p6',1,0,'',0,0,0),(270,103,11,401,0,'10.6.142.4',1325352523,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Course Not Running Exception','I was allotted the course EN 640 as Minor.\nHowever, at the time of registration, I get the following error:\nThere is no entry for this course in the current semester.\nWhereas, the following link on asc shows that course is running and does not clash with any of my other courses\' slot:\n<!-- m --><a class=\"postlink\" href=\"http://asc.iitb.ac.in/academic/utility/RunningCourses.jsp?deptcd=EN&amp;year=2011&amp;semester=2\">http://asc.iitb.ac.in/academic/utility/ ... semester=2</a><!-- m -->\nAnd this exception is a non-overridable one.\nHence, I cannot continue with my registration.\n\nPlease reply fast with an apt solution.','f73c1f1b5016045518c0140ddb88e5db',0,'','3mlnk8ku',1,0,'',0,0,0),(271,104,10,402,0,'10.6.70.132',1325358953,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Grade not allotted','I am a third year B.Tech. student from Civil Engineering and I registered for CE 397 (Seminar) as additional learning last semester. However, DUGC later decided that the seminar be shifted from third year to fourth year. Subsequently, third year (B.Tech. or DD) students were not allowed to take that course. \n\nI did NOT manually deregister from that course later in the semester. The ASC interface still shows that I &quot;have not been allotted a grade&quot; in that course. As a result, my new CPI has not been calculated and I was not allotted any minor.\n\nCould you please tell me how to get that course removed from my records? Also, how do I register for a minor now?\n\nThanks!  <!-- s:D --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon/biggrin.gif\" alt=\":D\" title=\"Very Happy\" /><!-- s:D -->','05a1f2e624008d8b75b5e19a3502a38a',0,'','1ltq27ax',1,0,'',0,0,0),(272,105,32,406,0,'10.5.11.179',1325400413,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','EN615 Minor course registration problem','I have been pre registered for EN 615 , but while verifying it shows this error message 	\'There is no entry for this course in the current semester \' even when this course is running in this sem','ab1ef54d6770408c40fb939b9a3210cc',0,'','2kw300fb',1,0,'',0,0,0),(273,106,8,124,0,'10.6.71.137',1325409194,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Tagging Query','1. Can we tag a Department course(starting with AE) as Institute elective?\n\n2. Can any course from outside the department be tagged as Institute elective?','0a0f4267521701fe487cd66a83d005be',0,'','15ozxj3z',1,0,'',0,0,0),(274,107,29,409,0,'10.7.164.17',1325410957,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','SJM courses slots.','The slots for most of the management courses are not given on the ASC. Can you please help?\nAnd can we take the SJM courses as insti electives?','fc4760dbcaaa41b476e3211bf624703f',0,'','32ih0edz',1,0,'',0,0,0),(275,108,11,323,0,'10.6.132.4',1325412865,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','registration exception','Hi,\nA friend of mine (CS BTech 2) is getting a registration exception when he registers for 48credits + an\naudit course but does not get any error when he registers for only 48 credits(without any audit course).\nHe cannot access the site, so has asked me to post.\nReply asap with an appropriate solution.','f71a559a427c8aa93796d96e065255f8',0,'','309pnlc6',1,0,'',0,0,0),(276,109,9,410,0,'10.7.22.223',1325414008,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','AN 605 slot','hi \nI want to take course from animation department as my insti elective butslot of animation courses has not been updated till now on asc site.','d7f3eac40f4fb636a3f5ff24770cce76',0,'','3qb7k6eu',1,0,'',0,0,0),(277,106,8,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325421156,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Tagging Query','you can take any course outside your department as insti elective. you need to take the permission of your HOD to take any dept course as Insti elective. \n\nhave you already done the course and planning to tag it in future or you want to take it now??','685a290ad8ba8a97ce9c3e38feff5993',0,'','301nb1ta',1,0,'',0,0,0),(278,109,9,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325421308,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: AN 605 slot','the department has not decided the slots yet. It will be done shortly (within 1-2 working days) as soon as they decide.','6f405797e778e9cbb7e3d74a05f2e65e',0,'','15fommzr',1,0,'',0,0,0),(279,104,10,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325421942,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Grade not allotted','please go to acad office ASAP as soon as possible and get the course deregistred manually. \n\nAs far as minor is concerned,  you need to take the permission of the course instructor to take a minor course.','7d60017261dc200e8711e5edd71325b5',0,'','1jr4xjt0',1,0,'',0,0,0),(280,103,11,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325422664,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Course Not Running Exception','on the ASC interface the course has not been given the tag \'M\' (which means you can take it as minor) as you can see for EN 610 and EN 604. We will look into this soon as there may be some prob with the bulletin. Meanwhile you register without this course and afterward make the required adjustment.','93dd293bf0819dd3ab9ca0dd205e4189',0,'','3u77ulrd',1,0,'',0,0,0),(281,108,11,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325422751,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: registration exception','can please tell what error is it showing exactly. also mail your problem to <!-- e --><a href=\"mailto:asc.help@iitb.ac.in\">asc.help@iitb.ac.in</a><!-- e -->','c13a7a6e1c3e967a283977676f2e38c7',0,'','3bwtkfwr',1,0,'',0,0,0),(282,101,28,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325422914,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Minor Query','No it can\'t be done. You will get an error that there is no entry for this course this semester. Minor courses are given tag \'M\'. So if you take any other course as minor interface will show an error.\n\nAlso you will not get the minor degree if you do not complete the courses from that \'prescribed\' set','b05ac8de7d845b8ea9986feb5f9f387a',0,'','2wfzjq9j',1,0,'',0,0,0),(283,84,29,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325422985,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Department Elective and Course Tagging','take it as additional learning now and later on tag it as insti elective','515c7ea6eca52d99be02e4c02972628c',0,'','6pl2l9wa',1,0,'',0,0,0),(284,107,29,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325423062,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: SJM courses slots.','yes you can take SJM courses as insti elective if you have done the required pre-requisites','be186eb64d6357e3a50d314ec33a2f2b',0,'','9mi413zz',1,0,'',0,0,0),(285,100,32,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325423118,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Error in registration','please mail this problem to <!-- e --><a href=\"mailto:asc.help@iitb.ac.in\">asc.help@iitb.ac.in</a><!-- e --> with the pic of the error','74ad2ed3ff829d401db90907c8179717',0,'','260xqgvk',1,0,'',0,0,0),(286,102,32,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325423318,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Retagging of courses','for final year students tagging interface will open 2 times. One in 2nd last sem (around mid august), second after the last sem.\n\nIf you will not take any course it will be shown as backlog, so its better to take an insti elective now to be on the safer side.','05b4f9797364634579562c7ba2bd2981',0,'','14kden2y',1,0,'',0,0,0),(287,105,32,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325423434,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: EN615 Minor course registration problem','The course is running but minor tag has not been given on the asc interface. This will be sorted out shortly. Meanwhile register without this course once. You can make the adjustments afterward','b19ad72d829786d8da7810cbbfbcd1a4',0,'','1ue1uwa1',1,0,'',0,0,0),(288,108,11,323,0,'10.6.132.4',1325426129,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: registration exception','The reply is:\n&quot;You have registered for more credits than allowed&quot;\n\nPS: He is a Category I student','d36ee2a33e41abe3902394d60e0bdb39',0,'','227b9pfm',1,0,'',0,0,0),(289,110,14,412,0,'10.7.164.15',1325435658,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Regarding tagging of courses','I had taken two courses of IDC as minor in 3rd and 4th sems. I want to tag them as insti electives. Will that be possible?\n\nPrashant \n3rd year','5d3f90fc816202144f61e9ec0d6c3164',0,'','4nlpe4f2',1,0,'',0,0,0),(290,102,32,399,0,'10.209.4.2',1325436388,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Retagging of courses','[quote=&quot;namanlahoty&quot;:34xywgep]\nIf you will not take any course it will be shown as backlog, so its better to take an insti elective now to be on the safer side.[/quote:34xywgep]\n\nOK, but that means having to do an additional credit course that will not end up being counted. I (and for that matter, anybody) would wish to avoid that. Also, if I have to take an insti elective now at any rate, what is the point of being able to retag that minor?\n\nThanks','69c261cbaea0711de631bb81bfb58193',0,'gA==','34xywgep',1,0,'',0,0,0),(291,110,14,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325436675,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Regarding tagging of courses','yes you can tag them as insti elective. But tagging interface will open only in your final year.','701fcffb7fc4bd3d9164088ab882288a',0,'','23ea4vzq',1,0,'',0,0,0),(292,106,8,124,0,'10.6.71.137',1325487784,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Tagging Query','I have one extra course from the department, done as an Additional Learning course. I have to do one institute elective in this semester(as this is the last semester.). So I was wondering if I can tag the extra course from department as Institute Elective.','612930355c9b4a4c46040895e526f1fb',0,'','3mhsg1yg',1,0,'',0,0,0),(293,111,32,414,0,'10.6.71.37',1325491129,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Tagging Interface','Hi!\n\nI just want to confirm few things regarding the course re-tagging.\n\n1. Will the tagging interface be opened in the next sem for 2008 Dual Degree Students? (It was opened for BTechs last sem by the way.)\n2. What do we need to tag PG Electives (the 4 PG electives that the Dual Degree Students need to do apart from DDP and honors)?','bbda62cbe91833f08020cef83ea0e722',0,'','1zxxvqx1',1,0,'',0,0,0),(294,112,12,150,0,'10.9.70.211',1325491493,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','CSE Minor','Hi\n\nThere is no 4th year CSE Minor course this semester. Is it possible to take a regular CSE course and have it tagged as a minor course? If so, who all do we need to take approval from for this.\n\nRuchir','37036f2dfdcd5fce1cadda2091996cae',0,'','3zs6a9qb',1,0,'',0,0,0),(295,113,9,265,0,'10.4.52.79',1325491791,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Registration for ME 406','Hi \n\nThe registration for ME 406 is showing an error &quot;null.java.pointer&quot;. \nPlease take this up with ASC and get it sorted out.\n\nRegards\nDhruv','6b96e9d167666820c71619c237acfb0d',0,'','1a1x9579',1,0,'',0,0,0),(296,106,8,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325492304,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Tagging Query','you cannot take a department course as institute elective unless your HOD approves. So to tag that course as insti elective, you should have permission of your HOD [b:2pm9uh10]at the time of tagging[/b:2pm9uh10]. \n\nI would suggest you to take an insti elective this sem as it may be possible that HOD doesn\'t approve that course as insti elective.','232ec4d609c159afcbbd47fa3f89b2e3',0,'QA==','2pm9uh10',1,0,'',0,0,0),(297,113,9,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325492368,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Registration for ME 406','please mail this problem along with a pic of the error to ASC at <!-- e --><a href=\"mailto:asc.help@iitb.ac.in\">asc.help@iitb.ac.in</a><!-- e -->','89492fa9ab81768ba4746b0954a45990',0,'','19w3jrun',1,0,'',0,0,0),(298,111,32,139,0,'10.199.2.27',1325493000,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Tagging Interface','1. yes. tagging has been approved by senate and it should be there next year also.\n\n2. Confirm with your DGsec if you have to do that course as Dept elective. If so then you have to tag it as department elective.','3fbb4f67e74c477fa5b5522b1a1679d6',0,'','1ykx7v7b',1,0,'',0,0,0),(299,106,8,124,0,'10.6.71.137',1325493421,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Tagging Query','Thanks for the advice! <!-- s:P --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon/razz.gif\" alt=\":P\" title=\"Razz\" /><!-- s:P -->','843f0d1c56390464752137032f0485b5',0,'','980gbyij',1,0,'',0,0,0),(300,114,32,326,0,'10.6.142.2',1325524642,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Normal course as minor','Apart from taking permission from the respective faculty, what all must be done if one wants to register a normal/non-minor course as a minor?','18ee165152a66168bffad95609f9249f',0,'','31yzq4ms',1,0,'',0,0,0),(301,114,32,139,0,'10.5.101.43',1325577879,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: Normal course as minor','you cannot take non-minor course as minor unless it has been approved by HOD and DUGC.','c18104b57fc35a244e8c3308b937328d',0,'','2a893n9s',1,0,'',0,0,0),(302,115,32,410,0,'10.7.22.225',1325586815,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','5 credit course as an insti elective','Can i take 5 credit course as my insti elective. Is it compulsory to complete 12 insti-elective credits','1dd1df79348fa58e1c4686976e78c50c',0,'','33e6mjii',1,0,'',0,0,0),(303,115,32,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325617785,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: 5 credit course as an insti elective','I would advise you not to do anything less than 12 credits as institute elective for the completion of your degree','eaf284ede3d6e972147dcc05a703a365',0,'','2pxlxejs',1,0,'',0,0,0),(304,112,12,61,0,'10.4.162.27',1325663029,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Re: CSE Minor','Please register for CS 416 directly for the time being.','57700740adb88273dbd45852fecd36a7',0,'','1nvyy9wf',1,0,'',0,0,0),(305,116,32,326,0,'10.6.142.2',1325671684,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Extension of course adjustment deadline','If it is no too much of a hassle, can the deadline for adjustment be extended to 11th, Wednesday(evening)? Since this Friday being a holiday makes it impossible to try out more than one course in slots 5 and 6 before the current deadline/final registration.','2cae51ff2549155002d1612208f6c1e8',0,'','269mdyzh',1,0,'',0,0,0);
